{"tid":1046734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖慎入］厭世揮手圍爐區","createTime":"2019-03-04T12:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T13:37:13.000Z","uid":57447,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9e644a83210946f3c530cd78aeff1d4b14921854","tid":1046734,"uid":57447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T12:47:17.000Z","msg":"睇返十年前啲相嘅自己<br />\n幾咁天真活潑 對世事充滿好奇同想像力<br />\n睇到啲閪相 就會好撚燥<br />\n<br />\n我係潮文成日講嗰啲啲人 如果下下心想事成就世界大亂<br />\n世上總有我依啲廢人<br />\n<br />\n成日以為自己可以做啲咩改變到<br />\n但係努力完一輪 就會有啲撚樣撥你冷水<br />\n依家只係不斷咁催眠自己 捱落去總有轉機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/203743_dd2dcd1834b9fb21154720f2cce8a605.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F203743_dd2dcd1834b9fb21154720f2cce8a605.png&h=5d2fb251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身體好多朋友，圈子其實都換過幾次，但係夾唔到就係夾唔到，好自卑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多我一個唔多 少我一個唔少<br />\n可以點"},{"pid":"03d446836491775954d110cd99bcebf219ab040b","tid":1046734,"uid":7988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T12:51:49.000Z","msg":"幾歲？男定女？"},{"pid":"ca616f50ad8bb67065998ab2762f29027a286994","tid":1046734,"uid":125380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T12:58:16.000Z","msg":"岩岩失戀 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e33c0b1033fbccc0f32b651791c1221bfc4f9d8","tid":1046734,"uid":219356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:00:57.000Z","msg":"好難同人夾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac879d170acd6433fc9fd555b9402e71e745c3f","tid":1046734,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8441afce0a3cbecdeb34afb